The Best of Youth;;2003;;R;;Drama,Romance;;8.5;;Marco Tullio Giordana;;Luigi Lo Cascio,Alessio Boni,Jasmine Trinca,Adriana Asti,Sonia Bergamasco,Fabrizio Gifuni,Maya Sansa,Valentina Carnelutti,Andrea Tidona,Lidia Vitale,Claudio Gioè,Paolo Bonanni,Giovanni Scifoni,Riccardo Scamarcio,Camilla Filippi,Mario Schiano,Michele Melega,Thérèse Vaddem;;Nicola and Matteo Carati are two brothers of Rome, who live the years from 1966 to 2000 and all the events which have signed this period. They begin their adventure, helping Giorgia, a young girl confined in an asylum. Then, after the flood of Florence, Nicola meets Giulia a talented piano player with a dangerous sympathy for the BR. Matteo, a rebel spirit entered in the police, will find the optimistic photographer Mirella. These four characters and many others will cross the years of terrorism and Tangentopoli.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0346336/